Core API Structure (REST)
Base URL: https://api.example.com/v1/ 
1. Medication Search/Lookup
Find drug products by name, strength, or type. 
Endpoint: /medication/search
Method: GET
Query Parameters:
q (string): Search query (e.g., "aspirin", "tylenol").
limit (int): Number of results.
form (string): Tablet, capsule, liquid.
Example Call: GET /v1/medication/search?q=aspirin&limit=5 
